    "title": "函数与方法",
    "category": "section",
    "text": "\"...\"\nfunction f end\n\n\"...\"\nf把 docstring \"...\" 添加给了函数 f。首选的语法是第一种，虽然两者是等价的。\"...\"\nf(x) = x\n\n\"...\"\nfunction f(x)\n    x\nend\n\n\"...\"\nf(x)把 docstring \"...\" 添加给了方法 f(::Any)。\"...\"\nf(x, y = 1) = x + y把 docstring \"...\" 添加给了两个方法，分别为 f(::Any) 和 f(::Any, ::Any)。"
